import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result == 1;

  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;

  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;

  //@ ensures \result != 0;

  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;

  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;

  public static int nondetInt() {

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;

  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;

  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

public class AlarmOutputs {
  public int isAudioDisabled = Verifier.nondetInt();
  public int notificationMessage = Verifier.nondetInt();

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;

  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;

  public static int nondetInt() {

  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

  //@ ensures \result > 1;

  //@ ensures \result == 0;

  public static int nondetInt() {

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ ensures \result < 1;

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;

  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

public class AlarmOutputs {
  public int isAudioDisabled = Verifier.nondetInt();

  //@ invariant logMessageId > highestLevelAlarm;

  //@ invariant logMessageId <= 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == 0;

  //@ invariant logMessageId >= 0;

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

public class AlarmOutputs {

  //@ invariant logMessageId <= 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == audioNotificationCommand;

  //@ invariant logMessageId >= audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > -1;
  public int logMessageId = Verifier.nondetInt();

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ invariant logMessageId <= audioNotificationCommand;

  //@ invariant logMessageId >= audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < -1;

  //@ invariant logMessageId == -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > -1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;

  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

public class AlarmOutputs {
  public int isAudioDisabled = Verifier.nondetInt();
  public int notificationMessage = Verifier.nondetInt();
  public int audioNotificationCommand = Verifier.nondetInt();
  public int highestLevelAlarm = Verifier.nondetInt();
  //@ invariant logMessageId > 1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > 0;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > audioNotificationCommand;
  //@ invariant logMessageId < -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId <= -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId == -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId != -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId >= -1;
  //@ invariant logMessageId > -1;
  public int logMessageId = Verifier.nondetInt();

  //@ requires \nonnullelements(args);
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    for(int i = 0; i < 10; i++)
      Verifier.nondetInt();
    AlarmOutputs a;
  }
}

import java.util.Random;

final class Verifier {
  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;
  //@ ensures \result == 1;
  //@ ensures \result != 1;
  //@ ensures \result >= 1;
  //@ ensures \result > 1;
  //@ ensures \result < 0;
  //@ ensures \result <= 0;
  //@ ensures \result == 0;
  //@ ensures \result != 0;
  //@ ensures \result >= 0;
  //@ ensures \result > 0;
  //@ ensures \result < -1;
  //@ ensures \result <= -1;
  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
    return new Random().nextInt();
  }
}

  //@ invariant logMessageId > -1;

  //@ ensures \result < 1;
  //@ ensures \result <= 1;

  //@ ensures \result == -1;
  //@ ensures \result != -1;
  //@ ensures \result >= -1;
  //@ ensures \result > -1;
  public static int nondetInt() {
